  • Non-Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Total Amount Of Damages: 0
  • Serious Incident Ind: No
  • Description: X RAYED SHIPMENT. THE OUTLINES APPEARD TO BE BATTERIES. SAW THERE WAS A UN3481 LITHIUM BATTERY MARK ON THE OUTSIDE, BUT THEY APPEARED TO BE BATTERIES BY THEMSELVES. PERFORMED A PHYSICAL SEARCH AND CONFIMED THAT THERE WERE 6 LITHIUM ION BATTERIES BY THEMSELVES, 100 WH EACH. NOT PACKED WITH OR CONTAINED IN EQUIPMENT. THESE WOULD HAVE BEEN ON BOARD A PASSENGER AIRCRAFT,
